abstract: President Obama was in Los Angeles for a taping of NBC's "The Tonight Show" on Tuesday in between mining for California gold at fund-raisers in Los Angeles and San Francisco.
snippet: President Obama was in Los Angeles for a taping of NBC's "The Tonight Show" on Tuesday in between mining for California gold at fund-raisers in Los Angeles and San Francisco.
lead_paragraph: LOS ANGELES -- With a morning taping of NBC's "The Tonight Show" on Tuesday, President Obama makes his fourth appearance on the couch opposite the host Jay Leno, in between mining for California gold at fund-raisers in Los Angeles and San Francisco.

headline.main: Obama Taps Into Hollywood in West Coast Swing
